<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cierre de sesiones activas</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-in-out;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #667eea, #764ba2);
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #5a67d8, #6b46c1);
        }

        .btn-outline-secondary {
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.9);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    {% block content %}
    <div class="card">
        <h3 class="text-center mb-4">ðŸšª Cierre de sesiones activas</h3>
        <p class="text-center mb-4">Detectamos que tienes sesiones activas en otros dispositivos. Â¿Quieres cerrarlas antes de continuar?</p>

        <form action="{{ url_for('auth.process_close_sessions') }}" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="temp_token" value="{{ temp_token }}">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100 mb-3">ðŸšª Cerrar sesiones y continuar</button>
        </form>

        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="{{ url_for('auth.login') }}" class="btn btn-outline-secondary w-100">Cancelar</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    {% endblock %}

</body>

</html>